title: For Sale:  Bushmaster XM15-E2S - A3 TELEF 16” M4 223-5.56mm plus MORE
postcontent:
Just wanted to start out by saying I am not someone who is trying to flip this gun.  I didn't get it for $750.00 and trying to gouge like MANY people on here that are trying to sell DPMS rifles, Bushmaster Flat Tops, etc. for $1400.00 plus.  Now that I've cleared that up, I also want to state that I'm not desperate to sell this gun.  I like it just fine, just was going to go in a different direction, but again, NOT DESPERATE.

Up for sale is a NIB, unfired, original boxed and factory oiled Bushmaster AR-15. It comes with a 30rd magazine, sling, lock, and the original manuals. This firearm features a 16” barrel with 1:9 twist, screw on/off flash suppressor, forward assist, a bayonet lug, sling mounts, and a 4-Position collapsible stock. The gun is also very accurate (For what it is.) because of the low recoil nature of the round. The gun is also very fun to shoot. (I know from experience.) The bolt assembly is all CNC machined, further enhancing the gun's reliability. A hard plastic case is also included with the gun.
